Package: saeSim
Type: Package
Title: Simulation Tools for Small Area Estimation
Date: 2014-05-12
Version: 0.3.1
Author: Sebastian Warnholz <Sebastian.Warnholz@fu-berlin.de>
Maintainer: Sebastian Warnholz <Sebastian.Warnholz@fu-berlin.de>
URL: wahani.github.io/saeSim
Depends:
    R(>= 3.0),
    methods
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    MASS,
    spdep
Suggests:
    testthat
Description: Tools for the simulation of data in the context of small area
    estimation. At the moment the tools are only intended to support
    model-based simulations. However, I believe the tools can be of use in any
    field of application.
